arts.ttl: Eintracht Frankfurt edge VfB Stuttgart in five-goal thriller
arts.sum: Chris Führich had a 98th-minute equaliser ruled out as Eintracht Frankfurt survived a thrilling VfB Stuttgart fightback at the MHPArena. The MHPArena set the stage for a captivating Bundesliga clash between Stuttgart and Eintracht Frankfurt, with both teams looking to solidify their positions in the top half of the table.

arts.ttl: Heartbreak for Stuttgart as Marmoush leads Frankfurt to 3-2 win despite fightback in Bundesliga
arts.sum: The Egypt forward took his tally to 11 goals in 10 league games this season, as many as Bayern Munich star Harry Kane, who scored three penalties to reach his tally. Omar Marmoush scored again and Eintracht Frankfurt survived a late fightback to win 3-2 at Stuttgart in the Bundesliga on Sunday.

arts.ttl: Drama galore as Frankfurt survive late Stuttgart fightback to seal victory
arts.sum: An enticing matchup between VfB Stuttgart and Eintracht Frankfurt entertained the masses this afternoon as the visitors ran out 3-2 winners despite Hoeneß' team dominating the first-half.

arts.ttl: Stuttgart vs. Frankfurt preview: Toppmöller's soaring Eagles looking to make huge statement
arts.sum: The 2023/24 Bundesliga sensations play host to the team seeking to take the league by storm this year in a mouth-watering clash on Sunday afternoon in the capital of Baden-Württemberg. The match that many Germans are perhaps looking forward to more than any other bears the hallmarks of a very exciting affair. A Frankfurt win could remove "VfB international" from the top-four conversation for now.
